templates","blackFridayBanners":"Black Friday banner templates","blackHistoryMonthBanners":"Black History Month banner templates","breadcrumbTitle":"Banner maker","breakingNewsBanners":"Breaking news banner templates","carnivalBanners":"Carnival banner templates","catBanners":"Cat banner templates","categoryRow1":"Logo maker","categoryRow2":"Poster maker","categoryRow3":"Flyer maker","categoryRow4":"Business card maker","categoryRow5":"Resume maker","categoryRow6":"Banner maker","cateringBanners":"Catering banner templates","colorfulBanners":"Colorful banner templates","coverSubtitle":"Create captivating banners and put your brand at the forefront","coverTitle":"Free Online Banner Maker","createFromScratch":"Create from scratch","cyberMondayBanners":"Cyber Monday banner templates","dentalBanners":"Dental banner templates","discordBanners":"Discord banner templates","discountBanners":"Discount banner templates","easterBanners":"Easter banner templates","emailBanners":"Email banner templates","facebookBanners":"Facebook banner templates","fallBanners":"Fall banner templates","faqsCategory1Content1":"A banner is a visual piece of content, often a mix of text and images, designed to grab attention and convey a message. It's commonly used in advertising, promotions, and web design to highlight information or encourage viewer action. To use it effectively, place it upfront where your target audience can easily see it.","faqsCategory1Content2":"Banner sizes vary depending on where you are going to use them. Digital banners often come in standard sizes like 728×90 pixels (leaderboards) or 300×250 pixels (medium rectangles). For printed banners, common dimensions are around 4×8 feet (1.2m×2.4m). The best banner size depends on the display space and the visibility you need.\n\u003c7\u003e\u003c3\u003e\u003c2\u003e\u003c5\u003eYouTube banner size:\u003c/5\u003e\u003c/2\u003e The maximum dimension for upload is 2560×1440 pixels with a 16:9 aspect ratio.\u003c/3\u003e\n\u003c3\u003e\u003c2\u003eTwitter banner size:\u003c/2\u003e The recommended banner dimensions for Twitter are 1500×500 pixels. This will ensure your image looks sharp across all devices.\u003c/3\u003e\n\u003c3\u003e\u003c2\u003eLinkedIn banner dimensions:\u003c/2\u003e A LinkedIn banner should be 1584×396 pixels to fit the profile header properly.\u003c/3\u003e\n\u003c3\u003e\u003c2\u003eTwitch banner size:\u003c/2\u003e Twitch recommends a banner size of 1920×480 pixels for profile headers, which will give your channel a professional look.\u003c/3\u003e\n\u003c3\u003e\u003c2\u003eDiscord banner size:\u003c/2\u003e The ideal banner dimensions for Discord are 1920×480 pixels, perfect for profile and server displays.\u003c/3\u003e\u003c/7\u003e","faqsCategory1Content3":"A banner should clearly display a headline to grab attention, a compelling visual or graphic to engage viewers, and a concise call to action guiding the audience on what to do next.","faqsCategory1Content4":"Sure. Browse all our banner logos by clicking on “See banner templates”, and find your best fit. Then, customize it to your liking within the online editor, from the colors to the text, and then download the final result in your preferred format.","faqsCategory1Content5":"Once your design is ready, hit the Download button, located within the upper right corner of the editor, and select the format between PNG, JPEG, or PDF, and wait a few moments until the download is complete.","faqsCategory1Title1":"What is a banner and how to use it?","faqsCategory1Title2":"What size is a banner?","faqsCategory1Title3":"What main information should a banner include?","faqsCategory1Title4":"Can I use a ready-made template?","faqsCategory1Title5":"How to download my final design?","fashionBanners":"Fashion banner templates","flagBanners":"Flag banner templates","floralBanners":"Floral banner templates","galaxyBanners":"Galaxy banner templates","gamingBanners":"Gaming banner templates","graduationBanners":"Graduation banner templates","greenBanners":"Green banner templates","gymBanners":"Gym banner templates","headingSectionName":"Banner maker","headingSubtitle":"Let your brand shine and draw attention by creating a banner for any occasion, for free. Customize any of our templates, or begin from scratch now.","headingTitle":"Easy banner creator for everyone","horizontalBanners":"Horizontal banner templates","leaderboardBanners":"Leaderboard banner templates","linkedinBanners":"LinkedIn banner templates","makersToGoSectionName":"More tools to go","makersToGoSubtitle":"Take your design skills to the next level with our online tools. We have all you need to create stunning visuals for any project you have in mind. Whether you’re a seasoned pro or a newbie to the design world, you’ll love our customization options","makersToGoTitle":"Top makers for endless creativity","mediumRectangleBanners":"Medium rectangle banner templates","newYearBanners":"New Year banner templates","ogDescription":"Design your message, visually. Our free banner maker allows you to create eye-catching designs that grab attention and deliver results. Make a banner in minutes, for free!","ogTitle":"Freepik | Free Banner Maker - Generate custom Banners online","oktoberfestBanners":"Oktoberfest banner templates","orangeBanners":"Orange banner templates","pinkBanners":"Pink banner templates","prideBanners":"Pride banner templates","purpleBanners":"Purple banner templates","rainbowBanners":"Rainbow banner templates","realEstateBanners":"Real estate banner templates","refractableBanners":"Retractable banner templates","relatedArticlesTitle":"Learn more about banners","restaurantBanners":"Restaurant banner templates","saleBanners":"Sale banner templates","seeAll":"See banner templates","seoDescription":"Design your message, visually. Our free banner maker allows you to create eye-catching designs that grab attention and deliver results. Make a banner in minutes, for free!","seoTitle":"Free Banner Maker - Generate custom Banners online | Freepik","simpleBanners":"Simple banner templates","sportsBanners":"Sports banners templates","squareBanners":"Square banner templates","summerBanners":"Summer banner templates","tabBusiness":"Business","tabEvents":"Events","tabSocialMedia":"Social Media","tabStyle":"Style","tabTopic":"Topic","thanksgivingBanners":"Thanksgiving banner templates","tumblrBanners":"Tumblr banner templates","twitchBanners":"Twitch banner templates","twitterBanners":"Twitter banner templates","useCase1Content":"Are you struggling to create eye-catching banners for your brand or event? If so, say goodbye to frustration and hello to the Banner Maker.\u003c1 /\u003e\u003c1 /\u003e\n\nUnleash your creativity and personalize your design with your message, add vibrant visuals, and tailor the colors to match your brand or theme. Once you’re done, simply download your masterpiece in \u003c2\u003ePNG, JPEG, or PDF\u003c/2\u003e, and start captivating your audience.","useCase1LinkLabel":"Create from scratch","useCase1Title":"The Banner generator, your best ally","useCase2Content":"Banners are a highly effective and visually appealing communication tool that can capture attention and convey messages. They are commonly used and strategically placed for advertising, marketing, celebrations, and special announcements.\u003c1 /\u003e\u003c1 /\u003e\n\nThey are incredibly versatile and come in a wide range of sizes, designs, and placements, making them ideal for both physical and digital spaces. Banners aren’t just decorative; they’re designed to spark thought, generate interest, and inspire viewers to take action.","useCase2LinkLabel":"Browse banner templates","useCase2Title":"What is the purpose of a banner?","useCase3Content":"Jump into a world of banner designs that are waiting to spark your creativity. Whether for your social media channels or your website, you’ll find a match.\u003c1 /\u003e\u003c1 /\u003e\n\nWith the help of the intuitive online editor, upload your brand logo, modify any colors, and drag and drop elements with ease. Your dream banner is just a few clicks away!","useCase3Title":"Explore banner templates and get inspired","useCase4Content":"\u003c2\u003e1. Main title:\u003c/2\u003e This is your attention-grabber, the big, bold text that first draws the eye.\u003c1 /\u003e\n\u003c2\u003e2. Visuals:\u003c/2\u003e Images or graphics that complement your text and make the banner attractive.\u003c1 /\u003e\n\u003c2\u003e3. Call to action:\u003c/2\u003e A nudge for the viewer, telling them what you’d like them to do next.\u003c1 /\u003e\n\u003c2\u003e4. Branding:\u003c/2\u003e Usually a logo or tagline, something that identifies the banner with your brand or organization.","useCase4Title":"Keep the banner structure in mind","useCase5Content":"\u003c2\u003eSimplify your message:\u003c/2\u003e Think about the main thing you want people to remember or do after seeing your banner. Stick to that and cut out the rest.\u003c1 /\u003e\n\u003c2\u003eChoose colors wisely:\u003c/2\u003e Make sure your text stands out against the background. Contrast is key for easy reading, even from a distance.\u003c1 /\u003e\n\u003c2\u003eOpt for high resolution images:\u003c/2\u003e If you’re using a photo or logo, ensure it’s high resolution, as blurry or pixelated pictures can ruin the final look.\u003c1 /\u003e\n\u003c2\u003eBe consistently you:\u003c/2\u003e Make sure your banner feels like part of your brand. You can achieve this by adhering to your brand’s color palette and font styles.","useCase5Title":"Discover more banner design tips","useCases2SectionName":"This is how you do it","useCases2Subtitle":"Discover how to design a captivating banner for social media or your website that’s all you. It’s quick and easy, even if you’ve never designed anything before.","useCases2Title":"Create a banner in (almost) no time","websiteBanners":"Website banner templates","wideSkyscraperBanners":"Wide skyscraper banner templates","winterBanners":"Winter banner templates","yellowBanners":"Yellow banner templates","youtubeBanners":"YouTube banner templates"},"collections":{"backToCollections":"Back to collections","backToMyCollections":"Back to my collections","browseAssets":"Browse assets","browseFreepik":"Browse Freepik and start adding assets to your collection","changesSavedSuccessfully":"Changes saved successfully","collectionCreatedSuccessfully":"Collection created successfully","collectionDescription":"Collection description","collectionFollowed":"Collection added to your collections","collectionNeedTitle":"You need to give your collection a title","collectionsCuratedTitle":"Best Premium Graphics on Freepik","collectionsTitle":"Free vectors, photos, and PSD downloads | Freepik","createCollection":"Create collection","delete":"Delete","deleteAdvise":"This willl permanently delete all the assets in this collection, but any liked items will still be available in Favorites","deleteCollection":"Delete collection","deleteCollectionQuestion":"Remove Collection?","deleteConfirmation":"Yes, delete","descriptionCollection":"Description of the collection","descriptionOptional":"Description (optional)","edit":"Edit","editCollection":"Edit collection","exploreTrendyCollections":"Explore Freepik's trendiest collections and find the perfect visual.","followers":"Followers","nameCollection":"Name collection","newCollection":"New collection","noCollections":"No collections to show yet!\nFind here any of our curated collections that you save","noCollectionsAvailable":"No collections available","pinterestEmptyCollectionError":"Add content to your collection before sharing","privateCollectionDescription":"The owner has made this collection private but you can still explore Freepik and discover images, moods, and styles to ignite your creativity","privateCollectionTitle":"Oh, this collection is no longer public","publicOption":"\u003c1\u003ePublic.\u003c/1\u003e Open for all to see and save, no edits","removeResourceQuestion":"Are you sure you want to remove this image?","removeResourceTitle":"Remove image from collection","saveCollection":"Save collection","shareLink":"Share link to the collection:","sharePrivateOption":"\u003c1\u003ePrivate.\u003c/1\u003e Only you can see this collection","sharePublicOption":"\u003c1\u003ePublic.\u003c/1\u003e Share link to allow access","titleCollection":"Title of the collection","trendingCollections":"Trending collections to boost your ideas","waitingAwesomeness":"This collection is still waiting for some awesomeness","wantToTry":"Collections let you do your own content curation and organize assets that belong together. Want to try?"},"templatesCommon":{"FAQ":"Frequently asked questions","artboardA4":"A4","artboardA5":"A5","artboardBusinessCard":"Business card","artboardDesktopWallpaper":"Desktop Wallpaper","artboardFacebookCover":"Facebook Cover","artboardFacebookPost":"Facebook Post","artboardInstagramPost":"Instagram Post","artboardInstagramStories":"Instagram Story","artboardXHeader":"X Header","artboardYoutubeThumbnail":"YouTube thumbnail","categoryRow1":"Logos","categoryRow2":"Posters","categoryRow3":"Flyers","categoryRow4":"Business cards","categoryRow5":"Resumes","categoryRow6":"Banners","chooseYourSettings":"Choose your settings","createNewDesign":"Create new design","faqsCategory1Content1":"A template is a predesigned layout you can customize for personal or professional use. It saves time and ensures your project looks polished and consistent.","faqsCategory1Content2":"Simply choose a template you like and explore the available options. Some templates include an \u003cb\u003eEdit online\u003c/b\u003e button that lets you customize the design instantly using \u003c1\u003eFreepik Designer\u003c/1\u003e. Others can be downloaded and opened in compatible design tools like Photoshop, Illustrator, or online editors.","faqsCategory1Content3":"If the template supports online editing, click \u003cb\u003eEdit online\u003c/b\u003e to open it directly in \u003c1\u003eFreepik Designer\u003c/1\u003e and customize it instantly—no software needed. You can also download the template and open it in compatible tools like Illustrator or Photoshop. Edit text, images, colors, and layout by accessing the file’s layers or groups. For best results, align your content properly, use consistent brand colors, and check spacing for visual balance.","faqsCategory1Content4":"Yes, many templates on Freepik are free to download. Free users can access a limited number of daily downloads. For more resources and unlimited access, upgrade to \u003c1\u003ePremium\u003c/1\u003e.","faqsCategory1Content5":"Yes, you can use Freepik templates for commercial projects if you comply with the \u003c1\u003elicense terms\u003c/1\u003e. Free templates may require attribution, while Premium ones do not.","faqsCategory1Content6":"Depending on the editing tool, you can export your customized design in formats like JPG, PNG, PDF, or SVG—ideal for print, web, or presentations.","faqsCategory1Content7":"Freepik allows a limited number of free downloads per day. Once downloaded, you can edit any template as many times as you like. Online editing through \u003c1\u003eFreepik Designer\u003c/1\u003e may be available for selected templates, even for free users.","faqsCategory1Content8":"Yes. Templates are provided in formats like PSD, AI, EPS, or editable formats for \u003c1\u003eFreepik Designer\u003c/1\u003e and other online editors, making them compatible with popular design tools like Photoshop, Illustrator, and browser-based platforms.","faqsCategory1Title1":"What is a template?","faqsCategory1Title2":"How do I use Freepik templates?","faqsCategory1Title3":"How do I edit a template from Freepik?","faqsCategory1Title4":"Can I download Freepik templates for free?","faqsCategory1Title5":"Can I use Freepik templates for commercial use?","faqsCategory1Title6":"In what formats can I export the designs?","faqsCategory1Title7":"How many templates can I edit for free?","faqsCateg