lfpage-banner-template_157573849","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10596346.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":157573849},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/twitter-post-dj-beat-template_49683525","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/8360368.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":49683525},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/cool-aesthetic-rectangle-banner-template_157573868","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10595083.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":157573868},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/elegant-aesthetic-luxury-jewelry-halfpage-banner-template_157573833","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10597066.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":157573833},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/cool-gradient-fitness-community-profile-discord-banner_81184277","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/8992547.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":81184277},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/modern-holographic-rectangle-banner-template_157573852","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10595096.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":157573852},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/aesthetic-gradient-beauty-leaderboard-banner-template_157573860","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10594943.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":157573860},{"url":"vector-mien-phi/elegant-hotel-leaderboard-banner-template_157573793","poster":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10597063.jpg","premium":false,"author":"Wepik","resourceId":157573793}],"relatedArticles":[{"id":1,"bg_image":"https://mediablog.cdnpk.net/sites/9/2022/06/COVER_BLOG_WebBanners_Freepik_1280x720.png","paragraph":{"en":"You come across banners every day, you probably even curse them sometimes, they annoy you, they get in the way of smooth browsing, they distract you from what really interests you, and they are ALWAYS there. But it’s very likely that what you hate today will turn out to be your greatest ally tomorrow, and together you will achieve the goals you set for yourselves.","es":"Te topas con ellos cada día, incluso seguramente los maldigas, te resultan molestos, no te dejan navegar de forma fluida, te distraen de lo que realmente te interesa, pero siempre están ahí. Casi con toda probabilidad, lo que hoy odias, mañana será tu gran aliado y juntos conseguiréis los objetivos que os propongáis."},"title":{"en":"What is a banner? Definition and types","es":"Qué es un banner? Definición y tipos"},"url":{"en":"https://www.freepik.com/blog/what-is-banner/","es":"https://www.freepik.com/blog/es/que-es-banner/"}},{"id":2,"bg_image":"https://mediablog.cdnpk.net/sites/9/2022/08/guide-to-create-a-perfect-banner-perfecto-.jpg","paragraph":{"en":"Banners are a part of our information-sharing staple diet. We consume its information daily, sometimes without even realizing it. They are frequent and driven by impulse! Today they are also a way to monetize websites and apps, and if you stick them in the right place, you will see some incredible results. It is, in some ways, a form of currency on the internet, and for you to take full advantage of this strange advertising subculture, your banner must stand out.","es":"Los banners forman parte de nuestro día a día. Consumimos su información habitualmente, a veces sin darnos cuenta. Son frecuentes y se crean a base de impulsos. También son una forma de monetizar los sitios web y las aplicaciones y, si se publican en el lugar correcto, los resultados que se obtienen son increíbles. En cierto modo, son un tipo de moneda en Internet. Para potenciar al máximo esta peculiar subcultura publicitaria, tu banner debe destacar."},"title":{"en":"How to make a banner","es":"Guía y ejemplos para crear el banner ideal"},"url":{"en":"https://www.freepik.com/blog/how-to-make-banner/","es":"https://www.freepik.com/blog/es/crea-banner-ideal/"}},{"id":3,"bg_image":"https://mediablog.cdnpk.net/sites/9/2023/10/social-media-advertising.jpg","paragraph":{"en":"Creating great online banner designs can be a challenge no matter what the occasion, even for experienced designers. Whether you’ve been designing digital content for years or just beginning to dip your toes into the world of graphic design, there are a few key elements that go into making banners that truly resonate and capture people’s attention.","es":"¿Quieres crear unos cuantos diseños de banners para San Patricio? Diseñar banners puede ser un tema complicado independientemente de para qué los quieras, incluso si eres un diseñador con experiencia. Tanto si has estado desarrollando contenido digital durante años o simplemente estás empezando en este mundillo, aquí encontrarás unos cuantos trucos para que puedas diseñar unos banners con los que te sientas identificado y que capten la atención de la gente."},"title":{"en":"What is social media advertising? Definition and sizes","es":"Publicidad en redes sociales: definición y tamaños"},"url":{"en":"https://www.freepik.com/blog/social-media-advertising/","es":"https://www.freepik.com/blog/es/publicidad-redes-sociales/"}}],"useCases1":[{"content":"useCase1Content","id":1,"image":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/10227458.jpg","title":"useCase1Title","link":{"label":"useCase1LinkLabel","href":"/designer/edit?template=new-artboard\u0026size=Large+rectangle+banner\u0026category_id=4966\u0026category_name=Banners"}},{"content":"useCase2Content","id":2,"image":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/9229687.jpg","title":"useCase2Title","link":{"label":"useCase2LinkLabel","href":"/mau/banner"}}],"useCases2":[{"content":"useCase3Content","id":3,"image":"https://fps.cdnpk.net/templates/media/categories/banner-maker/8031483.jpg","title":"useCase3Title"},{"content":"useCase4Content","id":4,